---
title: Spicy Shrimp Spaghetti & Steak with Zucchini, Lemony Breadcrumbs & Arugula-Parmesan Salad
description: This spin on fra diavolo features a thick and devilishly spicy marinara tossed with al dente spaghetti and topped with plump sautéed shrimp and zuccchini, plus lemony toasted breadcrumbs for crunch. You'll serve the pasta with perfectly seared bavette steak, a shower of Parmesan, and a bright, lemony arugula salad on the side.
